### =========================
### 🏠 OBTENER TODAS LAS PROPIEDADES
### =========================
GET http://localhost:3000/api/properties


### =========================
### 🔎 FILTRO: PROVINCIA
### =========================
GET http://localhost:3000/api/properties?province=Madrid


### =========================
### 🔎 FILTRO: CIUDAD
### =========================
GET http://localhost:3000/api/properties?city=Madrid


### =========================
### 🔎 FILTRO: TIPO
### =========================
GET http://localhost:3000/api/properties?propertytype=piso


### =========================
### 🏠 CREAR PROPIEDAD
### =========================
POST http://localhost:3000/api/properties
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
  "title": "Piso en Madrid",
  "price": 200000,
  "province": "Madrid",
  "city": "Madrid",
  "bedrooms": 3,
  "bathrooms": 2,
  "propertytype": "piso",
  "occupied": false,
  "reo": false
}


### =========================
### ✏️ ACTUALIZAR PROPIEDAD
### =========================
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/properties/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
  "title": "Piso actualizado",
  "price": 210000
}


### =========================
### ❌ ELIMINAR PROPIEDAD
### =========================
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/properties/1
Authorization: {{token}}